171],{"type":166,"tag":172,"props":173,"children":177},"a",{"href":174,"rel":175},"https://x.com/budibase?utm_campaign=Onboarding&utm_medium=email&_hsenc=p2ANqtz--6Ynd76E4FehE07-MjjIZWwvuH2B-KMkxdBPT1TJ5Eh4ci9Wy0q_RZYTIRBsGXz_09u4n_C8GiUe9f8mFjiC6Dj9B4sw&_hsmi=66516363&utm_content=66516363&utm_source=hs_automation",[176],"nofollow",[178],{"type":179,"value":180},"text","Twitter",{"type":166,"tag":182,"props":183,"children":184},"p",{},[185],{"type":179,"value":186},"2020 年那会儿 Budibase 从 SlackHQ 迁移到 Discord，发布了他的第一条推文，尽管点赞数量只有寥寥三个。",{"type":166,"tag":182,"props":188,"children":189},{},[190],{"type":166,"tag":191,"props":192,"children":194},"img",{"alt":160,"src":193},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501031913704.png",[],{"type":166,"tag":182,"props":196,"children":197},{},[198],{"type":179,"value":199},"推崇 Sarah Drasner 的空盒子概念，即“也许我们可以从一个空盒子开始，这个盒子只包含正在解决的问题的核心用例或问题”，而不是看到周围完整的网站或应用而感到自卑。Budibase 认为它是一个空盒子，为用户抽象了构建 Web 应用的复杂性。PRay 也是如此，并且应当在多用户交互上大有改进。",{"type":166,"tag":182,"props":201,"children":202},{},[203],{"type":179,"value":204},"Joe Johnston（应该是 budibase 成员）在 2020 年发表了 What is custom software development in 2025，讨论了“定制化软件开发”需求的广阔场景。",{"type":166,"tag":206,"props":207,"children":208},"blockquote",{},[209],{"type":166,"tag":182,"props":210,"children":211},{},[212],{"type":179,"value":213},"定制软件开发是指为特定问题、用户或人群设计、开发、部署、维护和提供软件支持的过程。理解定制软件开发的关键在于认识到正在开发的解决方案是为单一、特定的目的/问题量身定制的——通常无法通过现有的解决方案来解决。",{"type":166,"tag":182,"props":215,"children":216},{},[217],{"type":179,"value":218},"SaaS 软件（COTS 商业现货软件）单价比定制低，但远没有定制乃至自建来得灵活。",{"type":166,"tag":182,"props":220,"children":221},{},[222],{"type":179,"value":223},"“when COTS software did not solve the problem for SMEs, tools like Excel and Access were drafted in and a solution glued together”，Excel 作为从业者的信息交换工具，类似 Python、Lua 在游戏引擎中的胶水作用。",{"type":166,"tag":182,"props":225,"children":226},{},[227],{"type":179,"value":228},"今天正好是 2025 年 1 月，我认为 budibase 对软件开发的认识很有前瞻性。其观点也符合我的两点认识：第一，软件开发应该面向更广阔的 C 端，在知识爆炸并有势形成超级个体的时代，代码技能（实际上是指通过人机界面制定规则并实现需求）是全民必备的技能；第二，新时代的消费包含了新时代的创造，消费时间不仅仅通过娱乐，也可以包含创造性的方式，如同我的世界、乐高等。",{"type":166,"tag":182,"props":230,"children":231},{},[232],{"type":179,"value":233},"文章引用了 Percolate、Oribi、Monese 三个工具来说明定制软件如何解决问题，但没用过评价不了。实际上这可能只是为了文章的 SEO。",{"type":166,"tag":182,"props":235,"children":236},{},[237],{"type":179,"value":238},"2020-10-02 发布了一个暗黑风格的界面，是制作内容的暗黑风格，而不是 budibase 的。其本地的暗黑模式是在 2020-11-06 号发布的（已经过了公测前两周），不过这速度也太快了。",{"type":166,"tag":182,"props":240,"children":241},{},[242],{"type":179,"value":243},"有人发推推荐了一些产品，包括 budibase，剩下一些可能值得观摩的：",{"type":166,"tag":245,"props":246,"children":247},"ul",{},[248,259,269],{"type":166,"tag":249,"props":250,"children":251},"li",{},[252],{"type":166,"tag":172,"props":253,"children":256},{"href":254,"rel":255},"https://x.com/PoryHQ",[176],[257],{"type":179,"value":258},"PoryHQ",{"type":166,"tag":249,"props":260,"children":261},{},[262],{"type":166,"tag":172,"props":263,"children":266},{"href":264,"rel":265},"https://x.com/bildrHQ",[176],[267],{"type":179,"value":268},"bildrHQ",{"type":166,"tag":249,"props":270,"children":271},{},[272],{"type":166,"tag":172,"props":273,"children":276},{"href":274,"rel":275},"https://x.com/draftbit",[176],[277],{"type":179,"value":278},"draftbit",{"type":166,"tag":182,"props":280,"children":281},{},[282,284,291],{"type":179,"value":283},"有个 Tag 叫做 ",{"type":166,"tag":285,"props":286,"children":288},"code",{"className":287},[],[289],{"type":179,"value":290},"#100DaysOfNoCode",{"type":179,"value":292},"，看着不错。",{"type":166,"tag":182,"props":294,"children":295},{},[296],{"type":179,"value":297},"Bubibase 推荐了 Martin McKeveney 的 NoSQL 和 DynamoDB 的演讲。",{"type":166,"tag":182,"props":299,"children":300},{},[301],{"type":179,"value":302},"展示了一些预制的渐变色（UI 还可以优化）：",{"type":166,"tag":182,"props":304,"children":305},{},[306],{"type":166,"tag":191,"props":307,"children":309},{"alt":160,"src":308},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501031950748.png",[],{"type":166,"tag":182,"props":311,"children":312},{},[313],{"type":179,"value":314},"2020-10-22 发布了不推荐生产环境使用的公共测试版本。",{"type":166,"tag":182,"props":316,"children":317},{},[318],{"type":179,"value":319},"在什么是你建 Web App 时最喜欢的工作内容时，没有人投票给“测试”。不过，反向思考，能辅助用户做测试的工具可能也是很有市场的。",{"type":166,"tag":182,"props":321,"children":322},{},[323],{"type":166,"tag":191,"props":324,"children":326},{"alt":160,"src":325},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501031954506.png",[],{"type":166,"tag":182,"props":328,"children":329},{},[330],{"type":179,"value":331},"TechCrunch 的一篇 The No-Code Generation is arriving 文章中，根据“In the distant past, there was a proverbial “digital divide” that bifurcated workers into those who knew how to use computers and those who didn’t.”推演了今后数据分析工程在今后可能作为新的“数字鸿沟”出现以及带来的影响。而这正是过去几年（2017~2020）低代码发力的方向，AirTable 和 Retool 这种年轻的公司分别以 26 亿以及 10 亿美元的估值崛起。文章还提到了“而像 Bildr、Shogun、Bubble、Stacker”等公司，但是我没有用过。",{"type":166,"tag":182,"props":333,"children":334},{},[335,342],{"type":166,"tag":172,"props":336,"children":339},{"href":337,"rel":338},"https://nocodelist.co/",[176],[340],{"type":179,"value":341},"NocodeList",{"type":179,"value":343},"，收集了 300+ 无代码工具，而他本身就是一个很适合无代码建设的网站。",{"type":166,"tag":182,"props":345,"children":346},{},[347],{"type":166,"tag":191,"props":348,"children":350},{"alt":160,"src":349},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032006061.png",[],{"type":166,"tag":182,"props":352,"children":353},{},[354],{"type":179,"value":355},"数据看起来还不错，两周的公测信息。公测后两周的数据没有前两周好看。",{"type":166,"tag":182,"props":357,"children":358},{},[359],{"type":179,"value":360},"🔻 606 downloads\n🤖 619 apps created\n🚀 246 apps deployed",{"type":166,"tag":182,"props":362,"children":363},{},[364],{"type":179,"value":365},"在公测第三个月时，bb 积累了 3200+ 用户、2400+ 应用，以及 554 个部署的应用。",{"type":166,"tag":182,"props":367,"children":368},{},[369],{"type":179,"value":370},"2020-11-09 发布的图表功能，第一版的功能比较简单，但是很有视觉风格：",{"type":166,"tag":182,"props":372,"children":373},{},[374],{"type":166,"tag":191,"props":375,"children":377},{"alt":160,"src":376},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032011651.png",[],{"type":166,"tag":182,"props":379,"children":380},{},[381],{"type":179,"value":382},"2020-12-20 称自己是“open organization”，可以在 Github 上看到他们的项目路线图，甚至是参与讨论。这种事情（类似完成度的产品）在国内就算放到 2025 年也很难想象。",{"type":166,"tag":182,"props":384,"children":385},{},[386],{"type":179,"value":387},"2020-12-09 在 budibase，15 分钟就能创造一个 Winamp 风格的界面。也许包括功能？链接打不开了，无法验证。",{"type":166,"tag":182,"props":389,"children":390},{},[391],{"type":166,"tag":191,"props":392,"children":394},{"alt":160,"src":393},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032144479.png",[],{"type":166,"tag":182,"props":396,"children":397},{},[398],{"type":179,"value":399},"“将 Star 数量视为开源社区的货币”这一信念让 Joe Johnston 开始 budibase 的 Github 星星之旅。在 11~12 月间，其数量从 83 个增长到了接近 500，在图上来看这就是指数级别的增长！在博客中分享了其做法。时间来到次年 2 月，Star 数量超过 2000，两倍超越了他们的去年的既定目标。",{"type":166,"tag":245,"props":401,"children":402},{},[403,407,412,417],{"type":166,"tag":249,"props":404,"children":405},{},[406],{"type":179,"value":180},{"type":166,"tag":249,"props":408,"children":409},{},[410],{"type":179,"value":411},"邮件引导指向 Github 并告知路线图、代码都在 Github",{"type":166,"tag":249,"props":413,"children":414},{},[415],{"type":179,"value":416},"budibase 制作的项目支持 Github 调用",{"type":166,"tag":249,"props":418,"children":419},{},[420],{"type":179,"value":421},"更新 Readme",{"type":166,"tag":182,"props":423,"children":424},{},[425],{"type":179,"value":426},"而他们新的 Readme 也确实很有吸引力（“Build business apps 50x faster”）：",{"type":166,"tag":182,"props":428,"children":429},{},[430],{"type":166,"tag":191,"props":431,"children":433},{"alt":160,"src":432},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032149799.png",[],{"type":166,"tag":182,"props":435,"children":436},{},[437],{"type":179,"value":438},"“As companies, we often look outwards for growth, but looking inwards can provide op