r-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032340672.png",[],{"type":166,"tag":182,"props":638,"children":639},{},[640],{"type":179,"value":641},"在商业化上变得更加大胆，比如推出 Paid Only 功能。",{"type":166,"tag":182,"props":643,"children":644},{},[645],{"type":166,"tag":191,"props":646,"children":648},{"alt":160,"src":647},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032343927.png",[],{"type":166,"tag":182,"props":650,"children":651},{},[652],{"type":179,"value":653},"在最近（2024-11）的 3.0 更新中，他们解释了之后的路线，主要会包含 AI 相关功能的改进。",{"title":160,"searchDepth":655,"depth":655,"links":656},2,[657],{"id":169,"depth":655,"text":180},"markdown","content:6.maps:_products:budibase.md","content","6.maps/_products/budibase.md","6.maps/_products/budibase","md",[665,669],{"_path":666,"title":667,"description":668},"/maps/_products/bit","Bit","Bit 是一个组件驱动的开发工具，它可以帮助我们更好地管理组件。",{"_path":670,"title":671,"description":672},"/maps/_products/dynamo","Dynamo","Dynamo 原本是 Revit 中建筑信息模型 (BIM) 的附加模块，后来发展成熟，成为一个给设计师探索可视化编程、解决问题并自行制作工具的平台。",1742348694726]